(2, 63, 'Concept', 'concept', '<div>The design and construction of a visually appealing and contemporary home for a mid-50s married couple with two sons, 16 and 18 years old. We expect both children will no longer be living with us within 3-5 years.</div>\n<div><p>The house will be the home we live in as we enter retirement and beyond. It is anticipated that we will see out the remainder of our active lives in this home.</p>\n<p>The project site is situated in a community managed estate within the <a href=\"https://www.mercurekooindahwaters.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Visit the Kooindah Waters website\">Kooindah Waters golf resort</a>. The homes design, orientation and layout should be such as to take maximum advantage of the eastern aspect of the site which overlooks a natural billabong water course.</p></div>\n<h2>Overall Concept</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div><p>Open plan with abundant natural light</p></div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Passive heating/cooling principles with good cross flow ventilation</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Seamless integration and flow between indoor/outdoor living spaces</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Clever and inconspicuous storage and utility spaces</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Private and secluded with minimal opportunity to see in from street frontages</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/yootheme/landing-page-about-01.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/yootheme/landing-page-about-02.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n\n\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Budget</h2>\n<div><p>Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate.</p></div>\n<div>\n\n    \n        <h3>$800K + fees</h3>\n    \n    \n        <div><p>Construction</p></div>\n    \n    \n</div>\n<div>\n\n    \n        <h3>$25K-$30K</h3>\n    \n    \n        <div><p>Pool</p></div>\n    \n    \n</div>\n<div>\n\n    \n        <h3>$75K</h3>\n    \n    \n        <div><p>Outdoor Spaces</p></div>\n    \n    \n</div>\n<div>\n\n    \n        <h3>$75K</h3>\n    \n    \n        <div><p>Additional Landscaping</p></div>\n    \n    \n</div>\n<img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/yootheme/landing-page-living-room-01.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/yootheme/landing-page-living-room-02.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/yootheme/landing-page-living-room-03.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/yootheme/landing-page-living-room-04.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n\n\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n', '<!-- {\"name\":\"Landing Page\",\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"style\":\"primary\",\"width\":\"default\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"image\":\"\",\"image_size\":\"cover\",\"image_width\":\"2560\",\"css\":\"@media (max-width: 959px){\\n    \\n    .el-section > div {\\n        min-height: 450px !important;\\n    }\\n\\n}\\n\\n@media (max-width: 639px){\\n    \\n    .el-section > div {\\n        min-height: 240px !important;\\n    }\\n\\n}\",\"animation\":\"fade\",\"preserve_color\":false},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"row\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"media_overlay_gradient\":\"\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"text_color\":\"light\",\"position_sticky_breakpoint\":\"m\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"headline\",\"props\":{\"title_element\":\"h1\",\"title_style\":\"heading-medium\",\"text_align\":\"center\"},\"source\":{\"query\":{\"name\":\"article\"},