(5, 66, 'Living', 'living', '<img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/headers/title-bg-living.svg\" alt=\"\">\n<h2>Brief</h2>\n<div>\n\n    \n<h3>Last Revised</h3>\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n<div><p class=\"uk-text-lead\">We dont anticipate spending a lot of time in this space and its not a priority. It will primarily be used when entertaining. Resale appeal is a consideration so the space needs to work well within the context of the overall aesthetic.</p>\n<p>Aside from a lounge, one or two single seat chairs, a coffee table and a flat screen TV, we woould also like to be able to incorporate a fireplace as the ambience this will provide is very appealing to us.</p></div>\n<h3>Essential</h3>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Lounge suite</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Coffee table</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h3>Highly Desirable</h3>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Space for 3-4 seater lounge + 2 armchairs</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Space for large flat screen TV - either wall mount or freestanding</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Inbuilt gas fireplace (not freestanding). Wood or ethanol fueled would also be considered. If a wood fireplace, a dedicated space for fuel storage should be included</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div><p>Contemporary mantelpiece - could be a nice feature but only if it fits within the overall designaesthetic</p></div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Ceiling fan(s)</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h3>Desirable</h3>\n<div>\n\n    \n<div>Space for 4 seater lounge</div>\n\n</div>\n<h2>Impressions</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/living/gallery/1587618889217_1586830055887156342123649320181002HICKS53HOPETOUN0110retouch.jpeg\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>1587618889217 1586830055887156342123649320181002 HICKS 53 HOPETOUN 0110 Retouch</h3>\n\n\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/br