(10, 71, 'Office', 'office', '<img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/headers/title-bg-office.svg\" alt=\"\">\n<h2>Brief</h2>\n<div>\n\n    \n<h3>Last Revised</h3>\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n<div><p class=\"uk-text-lead\">The office is a crucial space and will be used daily in the running of our business. This room will see upwards of 60+ hours of use per week so the overall design and ambiance of this room is important to us as it will be heavily utilised.</p>\n<p>We would like the room to be more than just a practical utilitarian space in which to do work. If possible, in addition to a desk, we would like this space to be large enough for a full wall bookcase and a lounge allowing the room to also function as a private den or library.</p>\n<p>Land ratio restrictions and budget permitting, ideally we would like the office to be a small freestanding structure that could also function as a guest bedroom. In this situation a small ensuite bathroom should be incorporated into the design.</p></div>\n<h3>Essential</h3>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Private - must be enclosed with a locking door and not open plan or a study nook</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div><p>Large enough to fit an 1800mm modular stand-up desk</p></div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Abundant natural light and ventilation</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h3>Highly Desirable</h3>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Quiet - away from main living areas</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Large enough to fit additional furniture e.g. bookcase, TV + 2-3 seater couch</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Ability to open the room up with French, bi-fold or stacking doors</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Air conditioned</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Ceiling fan</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h3>Desirable</h3>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Separate from main house</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n